":"2021-04-27T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210426/5PFAWT2JOBHD7G5PIZ6Z243RJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210426%2F5PFAWT2JOBHD7G5PIZ6Z243RJE%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B62CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=be8bb218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210426%2F5PFAWT2JOBHD7G5PIZ6Z243RJE%2F&h=2324c9d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210426/5PFAWT2JOBHD7G5PIZ6Z243RJE/</a><br />\n<br />\n近日港人發現，從香港伺服器無法登陸台灣基督長老教會網站、民進黨及國防部國軍人才招募中心的網站。陸委會今（26日）表示，我方呼籲相關方面應確保香港民眾「知的權利」，勿一再高築、擴張網路長城，否則終將自損香港的國際形象與世界金融中心地位。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會指出，資訊自由是基本人權，也是香港作為國際城市的重要基石。<span class=\"red\">相關方面閹割香港資訊自由的作為，只會對外釋出香港愈益近似中國大陸之訊號。</span><br />\n<br />\n此前，2月香港多個網路供應商都無法連接促轉會官網，包括數碼通、香港寬頻、香港電訊、3電信及中國移動等網路供應商，均顯示「無法連線至此網站」，只能透過VPN經德國、美國等海外國家的伺服器才能登入。香港保安局當時同樣表示，對任何針對警方執法行動的揣測不作評論。（陳建瑜／台北報導）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:43:17.000Z","msg":"係衰過大陸"},{"pid":"2cea8ba370eec94b5b1a5bcc8444b311774aaeb9","tid":2505894,"uid":227628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:43:27.000Z","msg":"係衰過中国<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdfd3b9d708c461bad6b62c279b987a3b2b09f2","tid":2505894,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:46:01.000Z","msg":"正視聽，其實場運動已經贏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足俾人拉曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=黑警濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=國際核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我地贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=中共急了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=攬炒成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" cl